== 食虫性 ==
白环猪笼草最特别的是它只捕食[[白蚁|白蚁]]；大部分猪笼草不会对猎物进行选择。据植物学家[[马利斯·A·梅尔巴赫|马利斯·A·梅尔巴赫]]{{small|（Marlis A. Merbach）}}和他同事的所述，白环猪笼草是一种食性专一的[[食虫植物|食虫植物]]。<ref name=Merbach>Merbach, M.A., D.J. Merbach, U. Maschwitz, W.E. Booth, B. Fiala & G. Zizka 2002. Carnivorous plants: Mass march of termites into the deadly trap. ''Nature'' '''415''': 36–37. {{DOI|10.1038/415036a}}</ref><ref>Clarke, T. 2002. [http://www.nature.com/news/2002/020101/full/news020101-4.html Plant has taste for termites] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nature.com/news/2002/020101/full/news020101-4.html |date=20170422155943 }}. ''Nature News'', January 3, 2002. {{DOI|10.1038/news020101-4}}</ref><ref>Moran, J.A., M.A. Merbach, N.J. Livingston, C.M. Clarke & W.E. Booth 2001. {{PDFlink|[http://aob.oxfordjournals.org/cgi/reprint/88/2/307.pdf Termite prey specialization in the pitcher plant ''Nepenthes albomarginata'' - evidence from stable isotope analysis.]|185 KB}} ''Annals of Botany'' '''88''': 307–311.</ref><ref>Merbach, M.A., D.J. Merbach, W.E. Booth, U. Maschwitz, G. Zizka & B. Fiala 2000. A unique niche in plant carnivory: ''Nepenthes albomarginata'' feeds on epigaeically mass foraging termites. Tagungsband gtö 2000 13. Jahrestagung der Deutschen Gesellschaft für Tropenökologie 1–3. March 2000 in Würzburg Lehrstuhl für Tierökologie und Tropenbiologie Universität Würzburg. p. 105.</ref>

白环猪笼草具有独特的形态特征：在其唇下具一圈白色的绒毛。已捕获到白蚁的捕虫笼上的白色环状绒毛往往已消失。梅尔巴赫说：“有时会接连几日什么也没有发生，接着某个夜晚过后，捕虫笼内充满了白蚁，同时唇下的白毛也不见了。”

